# S3 storage classes

**Same 11-nines durability** — differ on availability, retrieval cost, min duration.

## Hot → warm

- **Standard** — instant, no min — the hot default
- **Intelligent-Tiering** — auto-tiers — unknown/shifting patterns
- **Standard-IA** — 30-day min + retrieval fee — backups
- **One Zone-IA** — single-AZ, cheaper — **reproducible data only**

## Archive — Glacier

- **Instant Retrieval** — 90-day min, **ms** — quarterly reads
- **Flexible Retrieval** — mins–hours — backups / DR
- **Deep Archive** — 180-day min, **12–48 h** — compliance

**Traps:** One Zone = no redundancy · IA/Glacier have **minimum billed durations**.
